And you can search in the book.

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:10.000
For example, if you want to know more, if you want to search for tables in the book, you can just type in that search box.

00:19:10.000 --> 00:19:11.000
For example, tab.

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:17.000
And you will see that your keyword will be highlighted on the page.

00:19:17.000 --> 00:19:20.000
So that's the search button.

00:19:20.000 --> 00:19:27.000
And here is the button for setting the themes and font size of the book.

00:19:27.000 --> 00:19:32.000
For example, you can make the font bigger or smaller.

00:19:32.000 --> 00:19:36.000
You can choose different font families.

00:19:36.000 --> 00:19:40.000
You can use serif or sans serif.

00:19:40.000 --> 00:19:47.000
You can set the white theme, sepia theme, night theme.

00:19:47.000 --> 00:19:50.000
So different themes.

00:19:50.000 --> 00:19:55.000
And as I mentioned, there's an edit button on the toolbar.

00:19:55.000 --> 00:20:00.000
Let me pop out the webpage in my web browser.

